Every now and then there's a social media challenge so ridiculous, you just have to laugh, and to participate in the latest one all you have to do is beat your bonnet. But not too hard, please. Or there could be something like a ... The trend started earlier this week when a video was passed along on social media accounts showing "the difference between a car and iMoto" Soon people were taking up the challenge with their own versions. In a clip a guy is seen hitting the bonnet of a Volvo and then hitting an older VW Polo that looks like it had work done on it. The streets were a mess in response. With some even sharing other hilarious car jokes. Others were hesitant to take the challenge...